MatrixSetValues: 2 (0- 0- 3+) (1+ 1+ 3+) [1 1 1] 0 6 0.0
MatrixSetValues: 3 (0- 0- 3+) (1+ 1+ 3+) [1 1 1] 0 6 0.0

# Bottom BCs
